body.name: FREY Natural Liquid Fabric Softener & Conditioner | Laundry Softener for Clothing | Works In All Machines + HE | Powered by Natural Ingredients | Jasmine Rose White Cedar Fragrance |50 Loads|Pack of 2
features: ✨ EXPERIENCE UNMATCHED SOFTNESS: Immerse yourself in the world of unparalleled softness with FREY's exceptional Laundry Softener. Our fabric softener liquid, combined with the captivating aroma of our laundry products, turns each wash into a luxurious treat that caresses your senses and your fabrics.

🌎 ECONOMICAL: Embrace efficiency with FREY's concentrated Fabric Softener. With a sizeable 16-ounce bottle, this liquid fabric softener provides a whopping 50 loads of pure indulgence. Saving you money and reducing waste, it's a choice that's both gentle on your wallet and the environment.

🍃 RENEW YOUR WARDROBE: Infuse new vitality into your garments with FREY's Fabric Softener Liquid. Say goodbye to stubborn odors that cling to your clothes, and welcome an era of freshness and comfort. Our laundry fabric softener breathes enchanting softness into every fiber, bringing back the joy in wearing your favorite outfits.

🌿 VERSATILE CARE FOR ALL FABRICS: Embrace the ultimate clothing care solution with FREY's Liquid Fabric Softener. Tailored for a wide array of fabrics – from delicate linens to durable synthetics – our laundry softener enriches each thread, granting a touchable softness that redefines your wardrobe experience.

🌻 RESPONSIBLE LUXURY: Choose FREY's Natural Fabric Softener for a touch of opulence that resonates with your values. Crafted with biodegradable, natural ingredients, this fabric conditioner aligns with your eco-conscious choices. Elevate your laundry while embracing a cleaner, greener approach to fabric care.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I Love It!
reviews.reviewText: My first package arrived with an active leak and about 1/4 cup worth of product pooled at the bags bottom. They scent was very strong.A replacement was scent out, no leaks or issues, but the scent still seemed strong. I've tried it a few times now, using different amounts, and no matter the amount used the scent hasn't been strong on the clothes. Only noticable fresh from the dryer or later if you directly smell an item of clothing.The scent pink scent is lovely and not too overly feminine. It's a soft floral with a light musk to me. If I could buy it as a perfume I would.

reviews.reviewText: Love, love this scent and the added softness to my linens is awesome! Thanks for an amazing product! Lasts a really long time in my linen closet!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I do not care for this over priced smelly stuff that they claim to do great.It smells awful and it doesn’t leave your clothes soft. I reran every single load of clothes that I used it in.I wouldn’t recommend this to anyone I care about.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 17, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Smells soooo gooood!
reviews.reviewText: This is a newer fragrance. I love it! It pairs well with the Frey detergents in the other fragrances as well! Makes my clothes soft and doesn't seem to negatively affect my sports clothes that aren't supposed to be washed with softeners (although I use less on those loads).
